headline: Agilent (A) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of life sciences tools company Agilent Technologies (NYSE:A) jumped 3.7% in the afternoon session after Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell indicated that interest rates could be cut, lifting stocks across sectors. The positive sentiment swept through Wall Street, with major indices like the Dow Jones Industrial Average, S&P 500, and Nasdaq all posting significant gains.
